瑞士"},{"pid":"5dae24960326472ccc5db4adcf5240730d947f8f","tid":569054,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ski<br />\n6 歲開始 瑞士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好勁!!<br />\n我都識一個香港雪友，佢係瑞士長大，所以滑咗好多年 ski，曾經喺 racing team 訓練。<br />\n上次有幸邀請到佢做咗分享會嘉賓分享 ski 技術~"},{"pid":"405259052ea2bab4ca846140eb40712ca3cc04d5","tid":569054,"uid":59617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"有朋友係日本教滑雪"},{"pid":"d72e1bac0ef53ac28f88d4abd275a48e9c314815","tid":569054,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T09:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友係日本教滑雪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀，好多香港教練係日本教滑雪。<br />\n粗略估計，我識得嘅應該有...起碼30個"},{"pid":"ea4e05c4bfa47b6b79778cbf01512c63b9ad9317","tid":569054,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd50f2ef0e97c3c6ac1b2858cd3ad89d069ca204","tid":569054,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"單板 <br />\n雙板<br />\n邊度學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"日本韓國，跟教練學"},{"pid":"a55099a4fab70a138a387897113ff4645e43be5c","tid":569054,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>單板 <br />\n雙板<br />\n邊度學</blockquote>日本韓國，跟教練學</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單板定雙板？<br />\n單板的話 韓國有 Team KASSI<br />\n堅勁嘅教練團隊!!"}]}